Package kindred.client.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    Class that defines a Unit's overall attributes that influence their performance during the game.
    Battle
    Calculates damage caused by a Unit to another Unit.
    Game
    Represents a game match where two Players battle against each other.
    Map
    Handles events related to a Map in the Game.
    Terrain
    Gives details about the vegetation of a Tile and how it affects a Unit's attributes.
    Tile
    Representing a piece of the Map, contains a Terrain and may hold up to one Unit.
    Unit
    Defines a Unit that a User can command, as well as its Attributes.
    UnitFactory
    Follows the Factory pattern to produce Units according to specifications.
